mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "Hot Line - Late News", "As I See It", "National Square Dance Convention", "Square Dance Diary", "A History of Square Dancing", "Smoother Dancing Poster", "Take a Good Look - When is a Cast Off not a Cast Off?", "The Dancers Walkthru", "Youth on the Square", "Roundancer Module", "Vox Saltator", "Ladies on the Square", "Style Lab - Star to a Wave", "Round the World of Square Dancing", "Callers/Teachers Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Chuck Bryant", "On the Record: Reviews", "Square Dance Date Book", and "Fashion Feature".
